            <h1><i class="fa fa-map-signs"></i> Welcome to YelpCamp!</h1>
            <p>View our hand-picked campgrounds from all over the world!</p>
            <p>
                 <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lrg" href="/campgrounds/new">Add New Campground</a>
            </p>
